description:
In this karaoke video, we're singing Love Divine, Love Excelling. If you're a fan of soulful and heartfelt Christian songs, then this video is for you!
Karaoke can be a lot of fun, and this video is a great way to get in the mood for a party or a night out. If you're a lover of hymn, then you'll love this karaoke video!

Title: Love Divine, All Loves Excelling
Author: Charles Wesley (1747)
Music performed  by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel..
